<H3> <TI>   Military Commander Reports Crop Destruction Figures </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Military Commander Reports Crop Destruction Figures </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WB0033C Mexico City EXCELSIOR STATES SECTION in Spanish 4 
Apr 94 pp 1, 4 </F>

<F P=103> 94WB0033C </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City EXCELSIOR STATES SECTION </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
