<TEXT>
Drug   Ties 

<F P=102> PA2104034294 Panama City Circuito RPC Television in Spanish 
2300 GMT 20 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2104034294 </F>
<F P=104>  Panama City Circuito RPC Television </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>
