<H3> <TI>   Joint Force Seizes 30 Tons of Hashish, Equipment, Weapons </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Joint Force Seizes 30 Tons of Hashish, Equipment, Weapons </PHRASE></F></HT>

