<H3> <TI>   Over 2 Million Mandrax Tablets Seized at Border With </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Over 2 Million Mandrax Tablets Seized at Border With </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Mozambique 

<F P=102>   MB2204174694 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1600 GMT 22 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB2204174694 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>
BFN 

  [Text] The Nelspruit narcotics bureau, in cooperation with 
the Swaziland police, have seized more than 2 million mandrax 
tablets with a street value of more than 30 million rands. 
Police spokesperson Colonel Schalk Pienaar said that the 
tablets had been found in a trailer at the Lomahasha border post 
between Swaziland and Mozambique. A 35-year-old man has been 
arrested in connection with the incident. 

