<F P=106> ["st."-signed report: "Marijuana in Ketchup"] </F>
  [Text] Vienna/Schwechat -- A suitcase with stinking fish, 
a putrid steppe animal, and African fruits from Lagos: At 
Vienna-Schwechat Airport, the drug squad headed by Colonel 
Alfred Rupf checked the strange luggage, where the four large 
ketchup cans were probably supposed to attract the least amount 
of attention. In fact, however, 19 kg of marijuana packed in 
plastic bags were found in the sauce. A suspect, who wanted to 
pick up the luggage, is under arrest. 

