<H3> <TI>   Police Arrest 9, Seize 19 Kg of Heroin in Istanbul, Van </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Police Arrest 9, Seize 19 Kg of Heroin in Istanbul, Van </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2304182994 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 21 apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2304182994 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video] </F>
  [Text] Eight members of two separate drug networks have 
been captured in Istanbul. The 13 kg heroin and 18 kg of 
hashish in their possession have been seized. According to 
information obtained from the Istanbul Directorate General, five 
members of a network preparing to smuggle drugs abroad were 
captured while in possession of 3 kg of heroin in Istanbul's 
Atakoy quarter. Meanwhile, three persons trying to sell drugs to 
the police acting as buyers have been captured in Ferikoy 
quarter. The 8 kg heroin and 17.5 kg hashish in their 
possession have been seized. An additional 2 kg of heroin and 
.5 kg of hashish were seized in searches conducted in hideouts 
shown by the smugglers. 
  [Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish at 1000 GMT on 22 
Apr reports: "Six kg of pure heroin were seized near Sevindik 
village in Gurpinar District in Van. One person was arrested. 
The heroin was hidden in the secret compartments of a car."] 

