  [Text] Tokyo, March 22 KYODO -- China's Forestry Minister 
Xu Youfang will visit Japan in May for talks on Japan's request 
for the loan of a pair of ibis for breeding, Prime Minister 
Morihiro Hosokawa told reporters during his return flight from 
