  [Text] The Inter Agency Task Force for Coastal 
Environmental Protection for the Ilocos region was recently 
activated during a coordinating conference held at the 
headquarters of the Naval District I in San Fernando, La Union. 
  Commodore Nicasio Blancas, naval district I commander, said 
the task force had chosen Lingayen Gulf as its pilot project. 
  The inter-agency task force was activated following a 
