<H3> <TI>   Minister on Processing Hungarian Nuclear Waste </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Minister on Processing Hungarian Nuclear Waste </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0204222894 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 
1800 GMT 2 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0204222894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


